# Stock Newsletter Analyst

Workspace root: `stock-newsletter-analyst/` (user home: `~/stock-newsletter-analyst`).

## Run in terminal (preferred)

```bash
cd ~/stock-newsletter-analyst
./scripts/setup.sh    # once
./scripts/start.sh    # Streamlit http://localhost:8503
./scripts/test-api.sh
```

## Do not

- Commit `.env`, `data/*.db`, or `.venv/`
- Paste API keys in chat

## Analysis pipeline

`ingest` → `analyze/companies.py` (Yahoo lookup) → `analyze/llm_core.py` (OpenAI) → `db/database.py`

Streamlit uses `analyze/llm.py` subprocess worker to avoid sandbox connection errors.

## Output schema

- `executive_summary` — short
- `detailed_summary` — 3–5 min read (~500–1200 words)
- `company_opinions` — per public ticker buy/hold/sell
